  1.6 "Source Code" for a work means the preferred form of the work for making changes to it.

  1.7 "Object Code" means any non-source form of a work.

  1.8 "Distribution" means to make available to others, regardless of the method.

  1.9 "Convey" means to communicate or make available to others, including, but not limited to, distribution and copying.

  1.10 "Network Use" means interacting with a user through a computer network, if the user has the ability to obtain the source code.

